headline: Royal Caribbean (RCL) Target Raised to $425 on Earnings Momentum
summary: We recently published an article titled 10 Best Cruise Stocks to Buy Right Now. On February 6, Tigress Financial raised its price target on Royal Caribbean Cruises Ltd. (NYSE:RCL) to $425 from $415 while reiterating a Buy rating. The firm highlighted that Royal Caribbean’s 2025 performance reflects a multi-year growth trajectory characterized by record revenue, […]
